Package: idlescreen-cosmic
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: IdleScreen <jerydleuck@gmail.com>
Depends: trance, trance-applet, trance-plugins-all
Recommends: trance-tui, trance-cli
Description: IdleScreen full stack for COSMIC Desktop
 Metapackage that installs the IdleScreen daemon (trance), the COSMIC
 panel applet (trance-applet), and all official saver plugins
 (trance-plugins-all). Recommends the optional TUI controller.
